## Bundled Font License

This project includes the Inter Bold font (UnPlex/fonts/Inter-Bold.ttf)
by Rasmus Andersson, licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.

The SIL Open Font License allows the font to be used, modified, and
redistributed freely, including in commercial projects, provided that:
